Package nl.naturalis.geneious.bold

Classes and interfaces dedicated to the BOLD Import operation.
Author:
Ayco Holleman
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoldDocumentOperation
    Hooks the BOLD Import operation into the Geneious plugin architecture.
    BoldImportConfig
    Contains the user input for BOLD imports.
    BoldImporter
    Manages and coordinates the import of BOLD files into Geneious.
    BoldImportOptions
    Sets up a Geneious dialog requesting user input for the BOLD Import operation.
    BoldKey
    The key used to store the documents selected by the user into an in-memory cache: the combination of the document's CRS registration number and marker.
    BoldNormalizer
    Normalizes BOLD source files so that they can be processed like any of the other types of source files (sample sheets and CRS files).
    BoldNoteFactory
    Produces a NaturalisNote from the data in a BoldRow.
    BoldRow
    Contains the values for a single row in a normalized BOLD file.
    MarkerMap
    Reads the marker mappings in the Tools -> Preferences panel and converts them to a Java HashMap.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    BoldColumn
    Symbolic constants for the columns in a normalized BOLD source file.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BoldNormalizationException
    Thrown when something goes wrong while a normalizing the BOLD file.
